metadata.name: School Break
metadata.description:
You are stepping into dangerous waters, a world of rogue kids in a parallel dimension, have created a microcosm of their own, and now they have to deal with the consequences of creating life.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
